item.description:
Join us for dinner on Friday nite after a week of hard work. Meet some new members and make new friends. Do you enjoy beef with watercress, soup dumplings, 3 cup chicken or maybe even stinky tofu? We can enjoy some shaved ice for dessert or go for froyo at Mixx which is 2 blocks away. We hope you can make it.

By T - take B train (Green Line) and get off at Comm. Ave and Harvard Ave intersection and walk a few blocks down to Brighton Ave.

Parking - is always tough in this area. Sometimes there are more spots on Brighton Ave towards Super 88/Hong Kong food court.
